{"tid":802244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：偷拍狂喪影港女腿胸　放IG大公開","createTime":"2018-09-01T10:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T19:20:43.000Z","uid":3189,"like":124,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"7f654e70933b8c209094259041ddd20afdc3f7ae","tid":802244,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20151126/photo/bkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_01p.jpg?20151126190216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20151126190216&h=561d3c42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20151126/photo/bkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_02b.jpg?20151126190216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20151126190216&h=e2e7c0cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n偷拍狂徒拍下多張女士穿平底鞋現腳筋的照片。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20151126/photo/bkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_03b.jpg?20151126190216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20151126190216&h=63c2a5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n部分是女士穿短裙熱褲的長腿照。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20151126/photo/bkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_04b.jpg?20151126190216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20151126190216&h=52da929f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n也有在港鐵車廂內，由下而上偷拍的女士腋下照。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20151126/photo/bkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_05b.jpg?20151126190216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20151126190216&h=d3fff7b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n穿著性感的年輕女子被近距離拍下胸部。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20151126/photo/bkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_06b.jpg?20151126190216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20151126180707834-1126_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20151126190216&h=8be15e90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民貼出一個IG公開帳戶，當中有逾4600多張偷拍女士身體不同部位以及走光的照片。 <br />\n<br />\n不同人有不同喜好，但假如有人公然在公眾地方偷拍他人的身體部位，甚至將偷拍照放上網公開，行為非常不要得。近日有網民就爆出有Instagram（下稱IG）用戶，瘋狂在大街上偷拍女士不同部位，如腳掌、大腿、胸部、腋下甚至是裙底春光，呼籲女士外出要小心可疑人士，好好保護自己。 <br />\n<br />\n上傳者指出，有變態狂徒把偷拍女士的照片發布在IG帳號內，於是決定公開其惡行。從多張照片所見，偷拍者曾在港鐵車廂及大街上偷拍女士們腳掌、腿部、腋下及胸部位置。偷拍者的部分照片更由下而上偷拍女士們的裙底春光。該批照片中有不少女士衣著都十分性感。 <br />\n<br />\n網民都覺得偷拍行為令人髮指，有人認出大多數照片都在觀塘工廠區一帶拍攝，隨即要大家廣傳，提醒女士出入該地區要多加留意，免遭「毒手」。另有網民看到貼文後，貼出一個IG公開帳戶，當中有逾4600多張偷拍女士身體不同部位的照片，部分照片與上傳者貼出的照片相同，故相信該帳戶極有可能為涉事者所有。 <br />\n<br />\n網民有話說 <br />\nDanny Sam：行家一出手，便知有沒有！ <br />\nLotus Francis：除咗男人咩都啱喎 <br />\nMan Wai Cheng：腳膠嘅心事 誰又猜得透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淺藍的天空：連阿婆腳都偷拍埋，好X變態喎 <br />\nSam Chan：見大部分相都觀塘區影，apm又有工廠嗰邊又有<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/nVRbRV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnVRbRV&d=q6KOYGt1kL0Myl74aCbbNp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=27a2c7ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/nVRbRV</a>"},{"pid":"389904fc3822cae4c27fe82ec21c3650e2fba20c","tid":802244,"uid":55386,"like":158,"dislike":2,"score":156,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"D 腳板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae570cfa07848de2a1de140e5a1da505e33c3e9e","tid":802244,"uid":89145,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:27:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f12788c3ba79e688a241cce14130e4c0b31d465","tid":802244,"uid"